Aurora, Ind., at a crook in the Ohio River overlooking tht town.; Photo, 
Hoosier Belle takes vacationers on sightseeing or dinner cruises.; Photo, 
Madison, steeped in Indiana history, enjoys the reputation of being a 
"19th-Century Williamsburg." MYRNA OLIVER; Map, Scenic Route, VICTOR KOTOWITZ / 
Los Angeles Times 
</P>
