Photo, Velma Galeano, left, and daughter, Ingrid Morrison, at their new 
$130,000 Fontana home. TODD ANDERSON / Los Angeles Times; Map, FONTANA, Los 
Angeles Times ; Table, AT A GLANCE 
</P>
