</P>
</SUBJECT>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA080689-0165 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 91653 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
August 6, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part 1; Page 1; Column 3; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
