<DOCID> 92391 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
August 6, 1989, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Book Review; Page 5; Book Review Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
27 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
